et]] |3 |2 |6 |2 | }}\n|R5={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Magnus Larsson]] |3 |6 |6 | | |T2P1=[[Ivo Heuberger]] |6 |4 |2 | | }}\n|}}\n\n==Quarterfinals==\n\n===United States vs. Netherlands===\n{{DavisCupbox\n|team1=United States\n|team2=Netherlands\n|venue=[[Palisades Tennis Club]], [[Newport Beach, California|Newport Beach, CA]], [[United States]] <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.daviscup.com/en/draws-results/tie.aspx?id=M-DC-1997-WG-M-USA-NED-01|title=United States v Netherlands|publisher=daviscup.com}}</ref>\n|date=4\u20136 April 1997\n|surface=Hard\n|score1=4\n|score2=1\n|R1={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Andre Agassi]] |7 |6 |7 | | |T2P1=[[Sjeng Schalken]] |6.059 |4 |6.019 | | }}\n|R2={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Jim Courier]] |4 |4 |6 |7 |6 |T2P1=[[Jan Siemerink]] |6 |6 |1 |6.039 |3 }}\n|R3={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Rick Leach]] |T1P2=[[Jonathan Stark (tennis)|Jonathan Stark]] |4 |4 |6 |3 | |T2P1=[[Jacco Eltingh]] |T2P2=[[Paul Haarhuis]] |6 |6 |3 |6 | }}\n|R4={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Andre Agassi]] |3 |3 |6 |6 |6 |T2P1=[[Jan Siemerink]] |6 |6 |3 |3 |3 }}\n|R5={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Jonathan Stark (tennis)|Jonathan Stark]] |6 |6 | | | |T2P1=[[Sjeng Schalken]] |4 |0 | | | }}\n|}}\n\n===Australia vs. Czech Republic===\n{{DavisCupbox\n|team1=Australia\n|team2=Czech Republic\n|venue=[[Memorial Drive Park]], [[Adelaide]], [[Australia]] <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.daviscup.com/en/draws-results/tie.aspx?id=M-DC-1997-WG-M-AUS-CZE-01|title=Australia v Czech Republic|publisher=daviscup.com}}</ref>\n|date=4\u20136 April 1997\n|surface=Grass\n|score1=5\n|score2=0\n|R1={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Pat Rafter]] |6 |7 |4 |6 | |T2P1=[[Martin Damm]] |1 |6.069 |6 |4 | }}\n|R2={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Mark Philippoussis]] |6 |6 |2 |6 | |T2P1=[[David Rikl]] |1 |4 |6 |4 | }}\n|R3={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Todd Woodbridge]] |T1P2=[[Mark Woodforde]] |4 |6 |7 |6 | |T2P1=[[Martin Damm]] |T2P2=[[David Rikl]] |6 |1 |5 |4 | }}\n|R4={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Mark Philippoussis]] |6 |6 | | | |T2P1=[[Martin Damm]] |4 |2 | | |