erg]] |T1P2=[[Mats Wilander]] |8 |6 |8 | | |T2P1=[[Miloslav Me\u010d\u00ed\u0159]] |T2P2=[[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]] |6 |4 |6 | | }}\n|R4={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Mats Wilander]] |6 |2 |4 |3 | |T2P1=[[Milan \u0160rejber]] |3 |6 |6 |6 | }}\n|R5={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Stefan Edberg]] |4 |6 |4 |6 |9 |T2P1=[[Miloslav Me\u010d\u00ed\u0159]] |6 |1 |6 |4 |7 }}\n}}\n\n===France vs. Australia===\n{{DavisCupbox\n|team1=France\n|team2=Australia\n|venue=[[Clermont-Ferrand Sports Hall|Maison des Sports]], [[Clermont-Ferrand]], [[France]] <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.daviscup.com/en/draws-results/tie.aspx?id=M-DC-1988-WG-M-AUS-FRA-01|title=France v Australia|publisher=daviscup.com}}</ref>\n|date=8\u201310 April 1988\n|surface=Clay (indoors)\n|score1=5\n|score2=0\n|R1={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Yannick Noah]] |3 |6 |6 |6 | |T2P1=[[Darren Cahill]] |6 |4 |4 |2 | }}\n|R2={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Henri Leconte]] |6 |7 |3 |7 |6 |T2P1=[[Mark Woodforde]] |3 |9 |6 |5 |0 }}\n|R3={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Guy Forget]] |T1P2=[[Yannick Noah]] |6 |7 |6 | | |T2P1=[[John Fitzgerald (tennis)|John Fitzgerald]] |T2P2=[[Wally Masur]] |3 |5 |4 | | }}\n|R4={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Henri Leconte]] |9 |7 | | | |T2P1=[[John Fitzgerald (tennis)|John Fitzgerald]] |7 |5 | | | }}\n|R5={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Yannick Noah]] |6 |6 | | | |T2P1=[[Mark Woodforde]] |2 |4 | | | }}\n}}\n\n===West Germany vs. Denmark===\n{{DavisCupbox\n|team1=West Germany\n|team2=Denmark\n|venue=[[Frankfurt]], [[West Germany]] <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.daviscup.com/en/draws-results/tie.aspx?id=M-DC-1988-WG-M-FRG-DEN-01|title=West Germany v Denmark|publisher=daviscup.com}}</ref>\n|date=8\u201310 April 1988\n|surface=Carpet (indoors)\n|score1=5\n|score2=0\n|R1={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Eric Jelen]] |6 |6 |3 |6 | |T2P1=[[Morten Christensen (tennis)|Morten Christensen]] |3 |3 |6 |2 | }}\n|R2={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Boris Becker]] |7 |6 |6 | | |T2P1=[[Michael Tauson]] |5 |4 |3 | | }}\n|R3={{ TennisMatch |T1P1=[[Boris Becker]] |T1P2=[[Eric